trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.DocumentPageView"></xref> that is associated with this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentPageViewAutomationPeer"></xref>.

Gets the string that uniquely identifies the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.DocumentPageView"></xref> that is associated with this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentPageViewAutomationPeer"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: The value of the automation identifier is the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationProperties.AutomationId%2A> property.
If this property is not set, this method gets the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Name%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Ha ez a tulajdonság nincs beállítva, ez a módszer lekérdezi a <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Name%2A>tulajdonság.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the automation identifier.

trans-unit.source: The collection of child elements of the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.DocumentPageView"></xref> that is associated with this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentPageViewAutomationPeer"></xref>.
